<ul>
<li>Microsoft and GoDaddy <a href="//thenextweb.com/microsoft/2014/09/23/microsoft-godaddy-launch-suite-tech-tools-help-small-businesses-get-online/">introduce a suite</a> of low-priced tech tools to help small businesses get online.</li>
<li>Could this <a href="//blog.hotspotshield.com/2014/09/22/googles-project-zero">Google&#8217;s Project Zero</a> make the Internet more secure?</li>
